INSERT INTO cache_entries (id, cache_key, data, created_at, expires_at, metadata)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            ON CONFLICT (cache_key) 
            DO UPDATE SET 
                data = EXCLUDED.data,
                created_at = EXCLUDED.created_at,
                expires_at = EXCLUDED.expires_at,
                metadata = EXCLUDED.metadata
